Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.39,0:00:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新机动战记-钢弹W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.59,0:00:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.06,0:00:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.60,0:00:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.71,0:00:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱着你被淋湿的肩膀 想温暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.92,0:00:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,颤抖的指尖 彷徨地在找什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.72,0:00:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的视线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.00,0:01:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲伤变为力量的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.44,0:01:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.11,0:01:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.75,0:01:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.45,0:01:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.96,0:01:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉财团藉着\N邀请和平的象征
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.56,0:01:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.30,0:01:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作为财团的代表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.67,0:01:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得到人们的支持
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.14,0:01:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令世界国家实现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.01,0:01:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另一方面，在宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.51,0:01:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反抗OZ殖民地式支配
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.25,0:01:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,称为白色獠牙的武装市民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.78,0:01:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在各个卫星纷纷起义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.58,0:01:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开始了独立运动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.49,0:01:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.96,0:01:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战乱的时代继续进一步加速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.56,0:02:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巨大变动的一刹那即将出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.53,0:02:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果那家伙死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.27,0:02:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世界国家和这种虚假的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.70,0:02:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就能被消灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.77,0:02:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.78,0:02:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要杀死你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.71,0:02:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第四十话\N[新的领导人]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.45,0:02:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们整理现状看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.32,0:02:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.72,0:02:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉正利用\N莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.69,0:02:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,统一其势力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.36,0:02:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.90,0:02:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜是否反过来利用罗姆斐拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.80,0:02:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但地球总算开始\N朝着和平起步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.24,0:02:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,问题是开始变得混沌的宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.81,0:02:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙里有五股势力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.51,0:02:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有那么多势力吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.98,0:02:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有，首先是白色獠牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.25,0:02:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是最大的问题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.72,0:02:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们怎样处置从OZ手上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.59,0:02:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抢过来的那艘巨大战舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.42,0:03:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们正继续建造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.32,0:03:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们想在和OZ宇宙军的战斗里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.96,0:03:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好使用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.09,0:03:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为OZ宇宙军是另一股势力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.93,0:03:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白色獠牙占上风也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.30,0:03:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙要塞巴尔吉也还健在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.87,0:03:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以上两者的战斗\N是更大的问题啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.64,0:03:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有...向以上两者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.28,0:03:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,展开游击战的钢弹们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.58,0:03:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道其他的两股势力是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.15,0:03:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那两者在称为势力方面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.32,0:03:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,稍为没有力量啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.05,0:03:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一股是附和白色獠牙\N的卫星居民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.62,0:03:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然在人数上是最多的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.69,0:03:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但他们没有表明意愿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.33,0:03:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,组织性和力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.23,0:03:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另一股是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.80,0:03:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然是我们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.23,0:03:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根据杰克斯的计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.70,0:03:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们要和钢弹们联手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.57,0:03:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，杰克斯那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.34,0:03:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去了地球后为何还不回来?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.75,0:04:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球正步向新的和平时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.72,0:04:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们服从莉莉娜女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.59,0:04:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乖乖放低武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.39,0:04:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么是和平?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.96,0:04:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们打算夺去我们的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.76,0:04:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,继续确立OZ的支配体制吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.69,0:04:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消灭扰乱和平的兵力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.64,0:04:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶!别怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.88,0:04:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.19,0:04:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.40,0:04:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.00,0:04:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹果然是帮我们消灭OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.97,0:05:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹为何会帮游击队?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.86,0:05:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜，身在罗姆斐拉之内的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.36,0:05:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毕竟只会产生虚假的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.93,0:05:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉或许会夺去我的自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.30,0:05:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，我甚至或许会被杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.40,0:05:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.84,0:05:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.94,0:05:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉会利用我继续战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.04,0:05:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.82,0:05:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.29,0:05:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在确立世界国家方面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.29,0:05:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我听说你有一套方针
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.29,0:05:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在，罗姆斐拉被认为是一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.69,0:05:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以武力支配人们的组织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.16,0:05:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是无可奈何的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.43,0:05:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉首先须要向人们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.97,0:06:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,展示正确和平的应有状态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.07,0:06:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你说出具体方案莉莉娜女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.71,0:06:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把派到世界各地维持治安的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.78,0:06:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ军力全部撤去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.51,0:06:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有异议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.98,0:06:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后，高声宣布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.82,0:06:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,武力支配结束的时代来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.69,0:06:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有异议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.19,0:06:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不得不说那其实是\N肤浅的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.93,0:06:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看来没想到散布各地的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.03,0:06:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,游击队或独立国家的军力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.90,0:06:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会成为我们的威胁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.00,0:06:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,威胁其实是罗姆斐拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.74,0:06:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,支配一方呼吁抛掉武器时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.91,0:06:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,支配者自己一定要先抛掉武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.31,0:06:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没问题吗?莉莉娜女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.51,0:06:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是罗姆斐拉财团所希望的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.75,0:06:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,支配世界的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.59,0:06:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从为世界带来和平的立场来看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.99,0:06:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉财团也到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.29,0:06:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要改变的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.46,0:07:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有传统的我们根本没必要改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.43,0:07:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是你个人的想法吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.33,0:07:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪尔麦优侯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.70,0:07:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.87,0:07:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是整个罗姆斐拉的想法吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.04,0:07:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉整体的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.44,0:07:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我打算代言呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.91,0:07:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗?各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.45,0:07:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，我们还未达到意见统一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.89,0:07:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜女王的意见也有道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.12,0:07:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别胡说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.56,0:07:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说罗姆斐拉会因为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.79,0:07:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个女孩的话而改变吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.84,0:07:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，我或许说得过份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.01,0:07:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是想各位注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.77,0:07:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉今后的方针
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.48,0:07:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只凭莉莉娜女王的意见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.28,0:07:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而决定的话会有问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.28,0:07:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,议题只是议题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.05,0:07:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.28,0:07:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在明天的财团总会里讨论吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.56,0:08:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最高干部会到此为止，散会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.29,0:08:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们只好放弃五飞那家伙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.43,0:08:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙打算独自迎战啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.10,0:08:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，回地球一次吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.70,0:08:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.07,0:08:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白色獠牙的部队散布在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.74,0:08:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,强行突破会很困难吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.58,0:08:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说就此不管白色獠牙吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.15,0:08:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.42,0:08:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该能令地球和宇宙和平共存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.68,0:08:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之后再和白色獠牙谈判就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.99,0:08:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\N白色獠牙一直继续武装
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.56,0:08:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然卫星的人不可以拿起武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.43,0:08:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.63,0:08:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是暗号通讯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.26,0:08:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是从这附近的空域传来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.27,0:08:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讯息里有死神这字眼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.77,0:08:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死神?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.84,0:08:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪欧，你听到吗?迪欧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.68,0:08:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大叔?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.01,0:08:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,霍华大叔吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.91,0:08:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看在以前的情谊上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.28,0:09:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你会再次雇用我吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.28,0:09:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,补给和修理我当然也会承包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.52,0:09:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,霍华你为何会在宇宙啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.09,0:09:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们有何打算?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.79,0:09:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连财团的主要干部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.13,0:09:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不听我的意见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.33,0:09:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家想服从那个莉莉娜吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.07,0:09:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为那就是莉莉娜陛下的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.97,0:09:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我为了巩固OZ的团结
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.87,0:09:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才拉拢莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.61,0:09:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但这样子她就变成障碍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.91,0:09:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事到如今…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.61,0:09:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啊，爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.05,0:09:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果莉莉娜陛下\N现在有什么不测
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.65,0:09:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爷爷你首先会被怀疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.25,0:09:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，现在的爷爷你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.56,0:09:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有说服大家的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.76,0:09:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是一针见血，桃乐丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.76,0:09:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，你讲得没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.46,0:09:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,财团正在动摇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.10,0:09:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,强大的领导人\N一定要团结所有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.00,0:09:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.91,0:09:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.07,0:10:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作为团结OZ和民众的象征就够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.38,0:10:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜陛下的和平路线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.45,0:10:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也认为不会就此顺利被接纳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.82,0:10:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定会需要武力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.52,0:10:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直维持着罗姆斐拉军力的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.05,0:10:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会大家认同为强大的领导人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.33,0:10:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜正想把\N罗姆斐拉的军力解体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.66,0:10:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爷爷你不是有OZ的宇宙军吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.47,0:10:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你叫我去宇宙吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.97,0:10:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在明天的财团总会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.91,0:10:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爷爷你的意见不会通过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.44,0:10:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家会同意\N莉莉娜陛下的意见吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.55,0:10:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比起打那种必输的仗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.72,0:10:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你应该准备军力应付下一场仗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.89,0:10:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你打算怎办?桃乐丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.89,0:10:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会留在莉莉娜陛下身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.93,0:10:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在她身边，战斗的风暴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.50,0:10:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定又会猛烈地刮起吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.84,0:11:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到我在这年纪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.27,0:11:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还要做前线指挥官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.74,0:11:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪尔麦优侯爵前往宇宙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.88,0:11:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,名目是为了\N牵制抬头的白色獠牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.42,0:11:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亲自前去指挥OZ宇宙军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.35,0:11:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,防范卫星叛军，改变航路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.29,0:11:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到达巴尔吉的时间会比原定迟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.99,0:11:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.56,0:11:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等着瞧，笨蛋们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.56,0:11:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我现在就证明给你们看\N我是对的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.88,0:11:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好极了，莉莉娜陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.95,0:11:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爷爷前往宇宙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.59,0:11:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.12,0:11:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最反对的人不会出席总会了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.26,0:11:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之后只有看莉莉娜陛下你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.76,0:12:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗?  迪尔麦优侯爵他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.06,0:12:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,时候差不多了，莉莉娜陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.97,0:12:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起去议事堂吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.30,0:12:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.25,0:12:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,时间到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.86,0:12:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是钢弹?不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.90,0:12:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，相信是钢弹05的机体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.36,0:12:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经冲破防卫网
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.83,0:12:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现正接近这艘[天秤座]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.44,0:12:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹不是为了卫星而战的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.81,0:12:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他为何攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.24,0:12:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以宇宙独立为目标的我们?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.65,0:12:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙不需要那种力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.29,0:13:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出动所有部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.46,0:13:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由于派了部队去攻击巴尔吉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.29,0:13:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在，天秤座周围
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.09,0:13:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,几乎没有护卫部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.76,0:13:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开动天秤座吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.70,0:13:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，天秤座还未…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.67,0:13:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主炮和推进装置\N以外应该能开动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.50,0:13:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使用天秤座的雷射炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.94,0:13:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位是全世界的领导人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.44,0:13:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，今后要继续担任领导人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.84,0:13:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉财团就一定要改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.95,0:14:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在，这个时代正继续改革
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.92,0:14:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对立为何不消失?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.89,0:14:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为异已的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.99,0:14:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,经常会成为对立的对象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.73,0:14:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要令对立消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.29,0:14:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就一定要所有人一条心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.83,0:14:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜，那很肤浅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.57,0:14:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我再次宣布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.91,0:14:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了令对立消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.81,0:14:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,建立和平的统一国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.28,0:14:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拥有最强力量的OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.68,0:14:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先就要放下武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.56,0:14:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.79,0:15:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赢了!钢弹失去踪影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.79,0:15:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.26,0:15:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，西迪兹上校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.93,0:15:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们确认到宇宙还有数部钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.27,0:15:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们今后也有可能再次来袭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.51,0:15:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,究竟为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.34,0:15:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹为何敌视我们?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.51,0:15:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为钢弹想为地球而战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.28,0:15:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星的真正敌人是地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.28,0:15:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宣战吧，上校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.29,0:15:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.52,0:15:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们打算先消灭OZ宇宙军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.42,0:15:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.56,0:15:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们正派遣部队前去巴尔吉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.03,0:15:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白色獠牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.53,0:15:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,仍然难以代表卫星全体的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.30,0:15:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是一个好机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.13,0:16:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令卫星意思统一的好机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.04,0:16:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是木偶也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.31,0:16:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不顾自己人的伤亡\N也要消灭敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.32,0:16:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们一样啊，那样和OZ无分别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.55,0:16:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是宇宙不需要的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.12,0:16:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世界统一并非只是包括地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.53,0:16:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,两种个体会产生对立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.13,0:16:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们要和宇宙合而为一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.50,0:16:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球和宇宙，宇宙和地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.50,0:16:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开始和平共存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.44,0:16:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球和宇宙和平共存?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.34,0:16:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,解除OZ的武装
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.97,0:16:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呼吁宇宙和平共存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.28,0:16:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望各位作为以往的领导人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.68,0:16:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接受这次改革
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.42,0:16:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.99,0:16:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.33,0:17:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，希洛，杀死我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.06,0:17:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恭喜你，莉莉娜女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.33,0:17:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉财团会遵从你而重生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.13,0:17:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.27,0:17:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.51,0:17:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧，莉莉娜，你做给我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.74,0:17:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会打倒我的敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.39,0:17:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,修理完毕后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.62,0:18:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沙漠钢弹也能在宇宙尽情战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.76,0:18:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多谢你，霍华先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.13,0:18:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也需要机动战士作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.83,0:18:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里有吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.33,0:18:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给予钢弹驾驶员\N使用的机体方面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.83,0:18:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连重武装钢弹的下落还不明啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.50,0:18:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起，我没有记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.54,0:18:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…我不是那意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.94,0:18:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,霍华，我不明白的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.41,0:18:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为何援助我们?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.38,0:18:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.65,0:18:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你究竟想用这艘舰做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.18,0:18:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实我也正为这问题而烦恼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.02,0:18:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什么意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.49,0:18:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，援助你们方面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.26,0:18:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是为了履行责任啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.66,0:18:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作为参予制造钢弹的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.90,0:18:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你曾参予制造钢弹?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.77,0:18:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实是制造托尔吉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.27,0:18:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的不知道\N杰克斯的下落吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.14,0:18:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至于他，我认为他还活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.88,0:18:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,霍华
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.34,0:18:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白色獠牙有事向地球宣布啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.61,0:19:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来是宣战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.35,0:19:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不出所料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.58,0:19:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们卫星渴望和平地\N得到自治权
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.99,0:19:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但地球总是以武力压迫我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.66,0:19:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,联合的时代是，OZ的时代是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.06,0:19:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而宣布建立\N世界国家的地球也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.90,0:19:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球方面的先锋是钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.10,0:19:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球方面使用钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.30,0:19:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻击渴望宇宙统一的我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.31,0:19:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了援助OZ宇宙军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.31,0:19:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么会的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.61,0:19:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能!那是藉口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.31,0:19:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你被利用了，五飞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.75,0:19:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，OZ宇宙军即将被消灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.65,0:19:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们已经派遣大型部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.09,0:19:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进攻OZ宇宙军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.86,0:19:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙是我们卫星居民的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.86,0:19:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发生什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.70,0:19:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是白色獠牙的大型部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.63,0:19:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为何会在这空域?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.53,0:19:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出动MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.02,0:20:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全速离开!逃进巴尔吉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.99,0:20:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…不行!会被追上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.31,0:20:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…我在这种地方…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.58,0:20:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪…迪尔麦优侯爵…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.45,0:20:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.26,0:20:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了不起，爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.79,0:20:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.26,0:20:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为爷爷你最后也在战场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.97,0:21:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身为勇敢的士兵而死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.50,0:21:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙统一时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.74,0:21:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们剩下的敌人就是地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.44,0:21:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们有大义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.41,0:21:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，我们迎接了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.45,0:21:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贯彻那大义的新领导人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.42,0:21:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新的领导人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.32,0:21:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球和宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.02,0:21:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这两个个体会产生对立吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.13,0:21:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的名字是米利亚尔特‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.30,0:21:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和宇宙对立的个体，地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.17,0:21:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在这里宣布要肃清它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.70,0:21:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.77,0:21:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么会的?杰克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.50,0:21:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.77,0:21:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.24,0:21:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在连罗姆斐拉\N也想改变的这时候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.01,0:21:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯，从次代\N显示的未来里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.11,0:21:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你选择了那条路吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.62,0:21:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从飞翼零式显示的未来里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.75,0:21:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我选择了的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.55,0:21:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这条路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.51,0:22:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.39,0:22:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心血来潮的找人出来\N只因为天气好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.39,0:22:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我一直等不到人\N你以为你是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.39,0:22:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你是跑过来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.39,0:22:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那也是应该的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.89,0:22:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love ! 那个惹人厌的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.39,0:23:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉弄人  是因为心理有爱意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.89,0:23:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love !  老是让人挂念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.39,0:23:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起\N我不该说出强人所难的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.39,0:23:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‧‧‧Just Love‧‧‧
