Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.69,0:23:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从财团代表的宝座上推下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.23,0:23:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这时，在宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.66,0:23:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗终于爆发了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.23,0:23:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是宇宙要塞-巴尔吉的攻防战
